    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You are a Remonstrator. The freedom of this world depends on you.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191140/extras/6661b18f954d65afdeb402cb2119e5e2.avif?t=1742851561\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191140/extras_big/6661b18f954d65afdeb402cb2119e5e2.avif?t=1742851561 width=800 height=226 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fights with crowds of police</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...Side by side with a crowd of the same people dissatisfied with the system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realistic combat system in the Beat'Em Up genre with police batons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unrealistic ragdoll physics of enemies flying away from your menace</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extremely realistic physics of desecration of city streets with impurities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Locations taken from real places and events... well, or not quite</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ranks and style points</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soundtrack based on popular songs</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191140/extras/3e8021b4a1aaed17a8afc54baaff379a.poster.avif?t=1742851561\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191140/extras/3e8021b4a1aaed17a8afc54baaff379a.webm?t=1742851561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191140/extras/3e8021b4a1aaed17a8afc54baaff379a.mp4?t=1742851561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Russian revolution</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Moscow, Bolotnaya Square, 2011</u></strong>: a crowd of aggressively-minded Muscovites rebelled against the regime. Take part in a mass brawl with the police and defeat the commander of the defense detachment with the call sign &quot;Bryansk-North&quot;!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle for the Capitol</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Washington, Capitol, 2020</strong></u>: Americans dissatisfied with the government have laid siege to the main government building. Break through the police fortifications and defeat Lieutenant Covfefe to get to the heart of the country!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Farmer's Fury</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Europe, 2020s</strong></u>: cornered by harsh laws, farmers are wreaking havoc on the city streets, armed with their tractors and manure delivery systems. Show the legislators what their restrictions are worth!</p>",
